### Google Maps API 測試
### 確保 backend/.env 中已設定 GOOGLE_MAPS_SERVER_KEY

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### =====================
### 1. Geocoding API - 地址轉座標
### =====================

### 測試：台北101
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/maps/geocode
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "address": "台北101"
}

### 測試：咖啡廳地址
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/maps/geocode
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "address": "台北市大安區復興南路一段253號"
}

### =====================
### 2. Reverse Geocoding - 座標轉地址
### =====================

### 測試：台北101的座標
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/maps/reverse-geocode
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "latitude": 25.0330,
  "longitude": 121.5654
}

### =====================
### 3. Places API - 搜尋附近咖啡廳
### =====================

### 測試：搜尋台北101附近的咖啡廳
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/maps/nearby
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "latitude": 25.0330,
  "longitude": 121.5654,
  "radius": 1000
}

### 測試：搜尋台北車站附近的咖啡廳
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/maps/nearby
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "latitude": 25.0478,
  "longitude": 121.5170,
  "radius": 500
}

### =====================
### 4. Places API - 文字搜尋
### =====================

### 測試：搜尋「信義區 咖啡廳」
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/maps/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "信義區"
}

### 測試：搜尋「大安區 辦公咖啡廳」
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/maps/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "大安區 辦公"
}

### =====================
### 5. Directions API - 路線規劃
### =====================

### 測試：從台北車站到台北101
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/maps/directions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "origin": { "lat": 25.0478, "lng": 121.5170 },
  "destination": { "lat": 25.0330, "lng": 121.5654 },
  "mode": "transit"
}

### 測試：步行路線
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/maps/directions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "origin": { "lat": 25.0478, "lng": 121.5170 },
  "destination": { "lat": 25.0330, "lng": 121.5654 },
  "mode": "walking"
}

